data.description: Welcome Home to 24538 Robinia Drive! This beautiful 3 bd 1.5bth colonial with 2 car attached garage and central air boasts tons of space for family and entertaining! Come be blown away by this amazing layout! Entering the home from the front porch you will be greeted by a lovely entryway with a staircase and large coat closet. The first floor includes a spacious living room decorated with sconces, a formal dining area, an eat-in kitchen, a half bath, and a family room with patio doors overlooking the meticulously landscaped backyard which includes a children's playset. Three nicely sized bedrooms and a full bathroom with jetted tub complete the second floor. There is a partially finished basement with a built-in bar and a separate laundry area on the lower level. Schedule your showing today!
